About This Demo

This demo has been designed using Houzez and Optima Express IDX Plugin from iHomefinder to display MLS listings. IDX is an industry standard that enables a real estate professional to display all of an MLSs property listings on their website, provided they in turn permit other MLS members to display their listings.

iHomefinder requires a license key to be activated. The license key wont be included if you buy Houzez, but it requires to be purchased separately.

Please note we dont receive any commission if you choose to buy an iHomeFinder license. Our recommendation is based on the quality of the product and is not based on any compensation.
